data.description: *CURRENTLY UNDER CONTRACT, SELLER ACCEPTING BACKUP OFFERS* Welcome your family to this move-in ready 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath home in the The Pines of Lynn Haven! This home was built in 2017 and features a spacious open floor plan with LVP flooring, lots of natural light, upgraded lighting fixtures and cabinets, quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances and a large island with breakfast bar. Upstairs, you will find this great bonus space that is perfect for relaxing or hanging out, or it could be a home office, or play room.  This home features 9ft tray ceilings, ample closet space, a spacious laundry room, sprinkler system and 2-car garage. Outside, you will find a beautifully landscaped backyard oasis featuring a privacy fence and a nice pergola with pavers and planters boxes.
